{"text_id":43793,"tokens":["The"," debate"," surrounding"," whether"," schools"," should"," require"," students"," to"," maintain"," a"," certain"," grade"," point"," average"," (","GPA",")"," in"," order"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," has"," sparked"," heated"," discussions"," in"," recent"," years","."," While"," proponents"," of"," the"," policy"," argue"," that"," it"," promotes"," academic"," excellence"," and"," accountability",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," it"," can"," have"," detrimental"," effects"," on"," students"," who"," struggle"," academically",","," face"," distractions"," or"," personal"," challenges",","," and"," aspire"," to"," pursue"," a"," career"," in"," sports",".","\n\n","First"," and"," foremost",","," requiring"," students"," to"," maintain"," a"," certain"," GPA"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," can"," be"," a"," significant"," barrier"," for"," students"," who"," face"," challenges"," in"," the"," classroom","."," For"," instance",","," students"," who"," struggle"," with"," learning"," disabilities",","," are"," English"," language"," learners",","," or"," come"," from"," low","-","income"," backgrounds"," may"," already"," be"," at"," a"," disadvantage","."," By"," requiring"," a"," certain"," GPA",","," schools"," may"," inadvertently"," perpetuate"," systemic"," inequalities"," and"," exacerbate"," existing"," academic"," struggles","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," phenomenon"," where"," students"," who"," need"," sports"," the"," most"," \u2013"," those"," who"," are"," already"," struggling"," academically"," \u2013"," are"," denied"," the"," opportunity"," to"," participate",","," further"," exacerb","ating"," their"," difficulties",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," requiring"," a"," certain"," GPA"," can"," create"," unnecessary"," stress"," and"," disillusion","ment"," among"," young"," athletes","."," Many"," students"," who"," participate"," in"," sports"," dream"," of"," pursuing"," a"," career"," in"," sports",","," whether"," at"," the"," collegiate"," or"," professional"," level","."," By"," tying"," eligibility"," to"," academics",","," schools"," may"," be"," discouraging"," students"," from"," pursuing"," their"," passions"," and"," ignoring"," their"," future"," career"," aspirations","."," This"," can"," have"," long","-","term"," consequences",","," such"," as"," decreased"," motivation"," and"," increased"," dropout"," rates",".","\n\n","Instead"," of"," requiring"," a"," certain"," GPA",","," schools"," could"," implement"," alternative"," solutions"," to"," ensure"," academic"," success"," and"," athletic"," participation","."," For"," instance",","," schools"," could"," provide"," additional"," academic"," support"," services",","," such"," as"," tutoring"," and"," mentorship"," programs",","," to"," help"," students"," who"," struggle"," academically","."," Additionally",","," schools"," could"," consider"," tiered"," eligibility"," requirements",","," allowing"," students"," who"," are"," struggling"," academically"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," while"," still"," meeting"," certain"," academic"," standards","."," By"," doing"," so",","," schools"," can"," promote"," academic"," excellence"," while"," still"," providing"," opportunities"," for"," students"," to"," engage"," in"," sports"," and"," develop"," their"," skills","."," Ultimately",","," it"," is"," crucial"," that"," schools"," strike"," a"," balance"," between"," academic"," rigor"," and"," athletic"," participation",","," acknowledging"," the"," unique"," challenges"," and"," aspirations"," of"," each"," student","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}